-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">?</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">Richard:一周前，由于她成绩差，我们处罚她，不准她外出，并且不允许她使用电话。但我知道，事实上，她的确使用了电话。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">Minuchin医生<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">:</span>你是怎么知道的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">?</span>你是如何变成一个侦探的<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">?</span>顺便问一句，你和<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; fon