ist-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">(</span>对<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Richard):</span>你妻子试图放松对<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitncy</span>的盯梢，但随后<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitney</span>会做一些相当于说“看着我<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">!</span>”的事，使得<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>再次上钩。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">母亲和女儿都没有理解地们白己的行为，是如何保持这个控制和反叛循环(contro1-and-rcbel cycle)在不断进行的。通过向另一个人说出对他们行为的评论，来间接挑战家庭成员，有时是非常有效的。这里我向<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Richard</span>描述了<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>的行为，这样可以使<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>不设防地倾听。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">Minuchin医生<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">(</span>继续<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">):</span>她们两个都被困住了。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitncy</span>需要<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>看着她，而<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>被<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitncy</span>钩住了，不得不观察<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitncy</span>，并对<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Whitney</span>做出回应。这是一个循环。你能帮助她们吗<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">?</span>你能将这两个人从恶性循环中解救出来吗<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">?</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">我挑战父亲，并让他介入，要求他成为一个非正式的协同治疗师。邀请家庭成员成为彼此的治疗者，是我治疗的一个特点。我相信这是保持家庭的积极变化的最可靠的途径。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">Richard:我知道<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>有可能在某些地方反应过度。几个月前，当我们试图建立惩罚规则时，<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>会大喊大叫，但一个小时以后她们就会一起去购物商场。<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">Mary</span>会感到自责并妥协。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 26px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; text-indent: 28px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-align: justify; font-family: dinprobold, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, 微软雅黑, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: 宋体;">Minuchin医生<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">:</span>在这种情况下你做了什么<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 22px; border: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&            </div>
